{"type": "article", "id": 25002, "title": "折叠椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-06T07:18:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115805HjI5VDbX0UTS2n6e.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是瑞典设计师 Jonas Forsman 为荷兰品牌  Moooi 推出的折叠椅，可以收成一个平面立在墙边以适应越来越小的居住空间。他采用了 3D 编织技术制作了椅子的靠背，很有弹性，椅子的座位则是一个软垫，收起来的时候正好收进了靠背的凹槽中。椅子的形态宽阔而舒适，有多种颜色搭配，很居家。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070211580363xtGDiNMfjAJ5Il.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115803gQ1W6TfOGbUSx493.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56303419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115804K5YyuhitkxmHTQsI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6741453\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115804Smv75CKxN69osOLP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021158049UxhgGKJD3onS81s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}